OL,6,FThree Welsh couples with almost 200
OL,7,Fyears of marriage between them are
OL,8,Fsharing their success in a long-
OL,9,Flasting relationship this
OL,11,F"A happy marriage and family", "a good
OL,12,Fsense of humour" and the ability to
OL,13,Fmix a "good gin and tonic" are some of
OL,14,Fthe secrets to a strong union,
OL,15,Faccording to the trio who all live at
OL,16,FCare UK's Llys Cyncoed home in Cardiff.
