OL,6,FHarold McMillan was prime minister and
OL,7,Fa young Elvis Presley was topping the
OL,8,Fcharts when Josephine and Aubrey
OL,9,FLangley, met at the Mostyn Dance Hall
OL,10,Fin north Wales in 1958.
OL,12,FThe couple had their first date in the
OL,13,Fback row of a cinema in Pontypool and
OL,14,Fwill mark their 64th wedding
OL,15,Fanniversary later this month.
OL,17,FAnother centenarian couple who have
OL,18,Fbeen married for more than 75 years,
OL,19,Fsaid their "loving family" had kept
OL,20,Ftheir union strong.
