OL,4,Creveal their secrets to success
OL,6,FOlwen and Arthur Hayward, aged 100 and
OL,7,F101 respectively, are the 15th married
OL,8,Fcouple in the UK where both spouses
OL,9,Fare aged over 100.
OL,11,FThe pair met in 1943 and enjoyed a
OL,12,Fscenic walk across the cliff top at
OL,13,FPennard, Gower for their first date.
OL,14,FThey now have two children, four
OL,15,Fgrandchildren and five great-
OL,16,Fgrandchildren.
