OL,4,Creveal their secrets to success
OL,6,F"Let your husband think he is the
OL,7,Fboss, as long as he obeys his wife",
OL,8,Fis the advice from Patricia Chesney
OL,9,Fwho has been married to John for 61
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FThey met on a Saturday night in Queen
OL,13,FStreet, Cardiff, in 1959 before tying
OL,14,Fthe knot four years later and have one
OL,15,Fdaughter.
OL,17,FStaff at Llys Cyncoed Care Home have
OL,18,Fpulled out all the stops to celebrate
OL,19,Fall of their couples' love stories
OL,20,Fwith a special dinner complete with
OL,21,FChampagne, cocktails and canapes.
