OL,6,FGeneral manager, Virgil Frincu, said:
OL,7,F"Olwen and Arthur, Jo and Aubrey, and
OL,8,FJohn and Patricia, are three love
OL,9,Fstories for the ages.
OL,11,F"Here at Llys Cyncoed, love is
OL,12,Fcertainly in the air, and it's been
OL,13,Fwonderful to encourage so many of the
OL,14,Fresidents to reminisce and share fond
OL,15,Fmemories from their own marriages and
OL,16,Frelationships."
